channel.title: Making skills max out at 99! [317 delta]
channel.description:
When i run my 317 delta source, I have a command "master" to get all stats maxed. but when I put 13,034,500 exp in every skill for the "master" commands, I still get 100 in stats.
I think the source goes from skill level 98 to 100, and skips 99? I have no idea why, its a cammypvp source though. I want to make all stats 99 instead of 100.
Any help, guides would be awesome.
Thanks!
